skdetail:

Invocation Name: dante fact
des:
This is a simple skill that tells us some interesting facts about Dante the poet of the monumental epic poem the Divine Comedy.
It is considered one of the most eminent works in the world literature. It presents the poet's imaginative vision of afterlife.
The skill can be invoked using 'Alexa, start Dante facts'.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
